{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_08_01_short",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜と遙子のユニットバトル終了後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "病院まで付き添ってもらってすみません\nくじいた足を一通り検査してもらいましたが……",
      "startTime": 6.6333333731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "足は捻挫も骨折もしていませんでした\n特に異常はないそうです",
      "startTime": 14.9333336274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。怜がステージで転倒した時は肝を冷やしたが\n何事もなくて安心したよ",
      "startTime": 22.0666669607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、過労気味だから大事を取って\nしばらく安静にするように言われました",
      "startTime": 29.3000014384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "過労か……。ユニットバトルに向けて\n毎日遅くまで居残り練習をしていたようだからな",
      "startTime": 36.4000014384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "無理してまた倒れたりしたら大変だ。念のためしばらく\n休養して、その間のサニピの活動は四人に任せよう",
      "startTime": 43.8666681051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私だけ仕事をお休みするなんて\nみんなに申し訳ないです",
      "startTime": 51.2666681051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんにはユニットバトルの時に\n散々迷惑を掛けたのに……",
      "startTime": 56.4333347718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで気に病まなくていいんじゃないか？\n遙子さんだって、こんなことで怒ったりしないさ",
      "startTime": 62.0333347718,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}